people have no objection to that.

278
00:30:18,368 --> 00:30:21,372
So don’t pay attention to frivolous things.

279
00:30:24,958 --> 00:30:30,190
Now, please put your left hand towards Me like this,

280
00:30:30,391 --> 00:30:32,940
which suggests symbolically

281
00:30:33,140 --> 00:30:36,540
that you desire to have your Realization.

282
00:30:44,414 --> 00:30:49,180
And those who do not want to have Realization should leave this hall,

283
00:30:53,618 --> 00:30:55,665
and leave others in peace,

284
00:30:57,334 --> 00:31:00,366
because they act negatively for others.

285
00:31:03,978 --> 00:31:06,876
Now please put your left hand towards Me like this,

286
00:31:10,654 --> 00:31:14,273
and put the right hand on your heart.

287
00:31:16,144 --> 00:31:19,100
As I said, in the heart resides the Spirit.

288
00:31:22,500 --> 00:31:25,340
Then you have to put your right hand

289
00:31:25,685 --> 00:31:28,443
on the upper part your abdomen

290
