on the left hand side.

291
00:31:35,577 --> 00:31:39,747
This is the centre of your mastery.

292
00:31:43,507 --> 00:31:48,214
Then you have to put your right hand in the lower part of your abdomen.

293
00:31:55,515 --> 00:31:58,900
This is the centre of

294
00:31:59,812 --> 00:32:04,776
the pure knowledge, manifesting through your central nervous system,

295
00:32:10,229 --> 00:32:12,780
the knowledge of divine laws.

296
00:32:15,123 --> 00:32:18,940
Then again we go back in the upper part of the abdomen,

297
00:32:19,140 --> 00:32:21,151
on the left hand side.

298
00:32:24,452 --> 00:32:26,780
Then we go again to the heart.

299
00:32:28,737 --> 00:32:31,660
Then we go, take our hand in

300
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:35,980
the corner of your neck and turn your head to the right.

301
00:32:41,093 --> 00:32:44,460
This is the center which catches when you feel guilty

302
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:47,940
and unnecessarily angry with yourself.

303
00:32:55,342 --> 00:32:58,757
You have to be very pleasantly placed towards yourself.

304
00:33:00,788 --> 00:33:04,460
Then we take our hand on

305
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:10,820
top of our, I mean on our forehead across, like this,

306
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:13,491
and press it on both the sides.

307
00:33:18,404 --> 00:33:22,597
Now we take this hand on the backside of our head,

308
00:33:22,797 --> 00:33:25,838
and put our head on this to rest and

309
00:33:26,038 --> 00:33:29,147
put it upward like that our head.

310
00:33:34,324 --> 00:33:39,540
Now we stretch our hand like this,

311
00:33:39,740 --> 00:33:42,198
and put the center of our hand,

312
00:33:42,398 --> 00:33:46,020
on top of the fontanel bone area.

313
00:33:48,255 --> 00:33:50,247
Right hand, right hand.

314
00:33:53,951 --> 00:33:56,622
And now move it,

315
00:33:56,823 --> 00:33:58,823
your scalp.

316
00:34:05,013 --> 00:34:08,788
Seven times. Keep your fingers up like that.

317
00:34:12,670 --> 00:34:15,460
Now, please close your eyes.

318
00:34:17,133 --> 00:34:21,825
I have already requested people who 
don’t want to do Sahaja Yoga, should go away.

319
00:34:22,026 --> 00:34:26,637
Please. There's not need to be so aggressive.

320
00:34:32,556 --> 00:34:34,556
Please.

321
00:34:36,944 --> 00:34:39,461
Still they don’t want to go; it’s very wrong

322
00:34:39,661 --> 00:34:41,661
and very aggressive.

323
00:34:44,531 --> 00:34:47,939
You cannot look at other people when you are not doing it.

324
00:35:11,090 --> 00:35:13,090
Thank you very much.

325
00:35:27,245 --> 00:35:29,829
Now, please close your eyes.

326
00:35:32,979 --> 00:35:37,660
Don’t open your eyes. Put both the feet parallel on the Mother Earth.

327
00:35:42,856 --> 00:35:45,998
Until I tell you don’t open your eyes.

328
00:35:49,081 --> 00:35:52,235
Now please put your left hand towards Me and right hand

329
00:35:52,436 --> 00:35:54,498
on your heart.

330
00:35:58,424 --> 00:36:03,100
Now here ask Me a very fundamental question.

331
00:36:07,419 --> 00:36:11,500
You may call Me Shri Mataji or you can call Me Mother.

332
00:36:11,700 --> 00:36:14,562
“Mother am I the Spirit?”

333
00:36:14,762 --> 00:36:17,300
Ask this question three times.

334
00:36:33,406 --> 00:36:38,300
Now, if you are the Spirit,

335
00:36:38,500 --> 00:36:40,417
you are your master.

336
00:36:40,618 --> 00:36:45,140
So put your right hand in the upper part of your abdomen,

337
00:36:45,340 --> 00:36:48,540
the left hand side and ask another fundamental question,

338
00:36:48,740 --> 00:36:52,420
“Mother am I my own master?” Ask three times.

339
00:37:08,904 --> 00:37:11,100
Now you are free people.

340
00:37:11,300 --> 00:37:14,340
I cannot force on you anything,

341
00:37:14,540 --> 00:37:17,700
leave alone the pure knowledge of the Divine.

342
00:37:17,900 --> 00:37:20,420
So you have to ask for it.

343
00:37:30,737 --> 00:37:36,019
So please bring your right hand
in the lower part of your abdomen,

344
00:37:36,322 --> 00:37:38,341
in the left hand side.

345
00:37:42,332 --> 00:37:44,336
And now please say,

346
00:37:44,536 --> 00:37:49,389
“Mother, please give me pure knowledge of the Divine”.

347
00:37:55,624 --> 00:37:57,738
Please say it six times.

348
00:37:59,351 --> 00:38:01,860
There are six petals to this center.

349
00:38:22,617 --> 00:38:27,691
Now as soon as you say these things,

350
00:38:27,891 --> 00:38:30,580
your Kundalini starts moving.

351
00:38:36,647 --> 00:38:39,340
To facilitate Her movement,

352
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:43,043
please raise your hand to the upper center,

353
00:38:43,243 --> 00:38:48,605
which is in the upper portion of your abdomen, on the left hand side.

354
00:38:54,715 --> 00:38:58,180
Now, here, you have to say

355
00:38:58,991 --> 00:39:01,148
with full confidence

356
00:39:01,349 --> 00:39:04,820
to facilitate the movement of the Kundalini,

357
00:39:05,747 --> 00:39:10,432
“Mother I am my own master”. Say it ten times.

358
00:39:35,021 --> 00:39:38,500
Now you have to know the greatest truth about you

359
00:39:38,700 --> 00:39:42,935
is that you are the Spirit.

360
00:39:49,247 --> 00:39:53,356
You are not this body, you are not this conditioning,

361
00:39:53,556 --> 00:39:57,100
not this ego, not this mind.

362
00:40:03,667 --> 00:40:05,820
But you are the Spirit.

363
00:40:06,845 --> 00:40:10,660
So now please put your hand on your heart.

364
00:40:13,747 --> 00:40:16,260
And with full confidence say,

365
00:40:16,460 --> 00:40:20,340
twelve times, “Mother I am the Spirit”.

366
00:40:28,677 --> 00:40:30,831
Have full confidence.

367
00:41:03,155 --> 00:41:08,380
Now the Divine is the ocean of love

368
00:41:08,580 --> 00:41:10,240
and compassion.

369
00:41:10,440 --> 00:41:15,060
But above all It is the ocean of forgiveness.

370
00:41:23,637 --> 00:41:27,841
Above all it is the forgiveness,

371
00:41:28,041 --> 00:41:33,290
then you cannot make any mistakes which can’t be engulfed

372
00:41:33,490 --> 00:41:37,820
by this great power of forgiveness of God.

373
00:41:43,832 --> 00:41:46,860
So please first forgive yourself.

374
00:41:50,958 --> 00:41:52,961
You have to love yourself

375
00:41:53,161 --> 00:41:56,540
and you have to be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

376
00:42:01,393 --> 00:42:06,340
Now put your hand on your shoulder

377
00:42:07,210 --> 00:42:11,580
between the neck and your shoulder,

378
00:42:11,780 --> 00:42:16,740
in the corner, and put your head to your right.

379
00:42:24,123 --> 00:42:26,660
Here now you have to say,

380
00:42:26,860 --> 00:42:28,940
with full confidence

381
00:42:29,897 --> 00:42:31,940
for sixteen times,

382
00:42:32,140 --> 00:42:37,100
“Mother I am not guilty at all”.

383
00:42:47,240 --> 00:42:49,500
Sixteen times.

384
00:42:51,431 --> 00:42:55,020
Now those who still want to feel guilty can punish themselves

385
00:42:55,220 --> 00:42:57,657
by saying it 108 times.

386
00:43:34,606 --> 00:43:38,684
Now please take your hand

387
00:43:38,884 --> 00:43:41,540
on top of your forehead across

388
00:43:41,740 --> 00:43:44,220
and bend your head a little.

389
00:43:50,864 --> 00:43:53,300
Here you have to say

390
00:43:54,495 --> 00:43:56,740
from your heart,

391
00:43:57,014 --> 00:43:59,860
“Mother I forgive everyone”.

392
00:44:05,712 --> 00:44:10,140
If you say it is difficult to forgive then know that it is a myth,

393
00:44:10,340 --> 00:44:13,140
whether you forgive or if you don’t forgive.

394
00:44:18,963 --> 00:44:21,380
But if you do not forgive,

395
00:44:21,580 --> 00:44:24,260
then you play into wrong hands.

396
00:44:28,296 --> 00:44:31,271
Yesterday I saw many people didn’t get Realization,

397
00:44:31,471 --> 00:44:33,660
and when they came to Me and they said,

398
00:44:33,860 --> 00:44:38,020
“Mother I forgive everyone”, they got it. So please do it now.

399
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:52,500
Forgive everything,

400
00:44:54,676 --> 00:44:56,676
everyone.

401
00:44:58,994 --> 00:45:02,740
Now, take your hand on the back side of your head

402
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:06,968
and put back your head, resting on that hand.

403
00:45:13,396 --> 00:45:18,302
Here you have to say without feeling guilty,

404
00:45:18,806 --> 00:45:20,900
“Mother”,

405
00:45:22,285 --> 00:45:24,820
or “the Divine

406
00:45:25,020 --> 00:45:28,678
if I have done any mistakes please forgive me”,

407
00:45:28,879 --> 00:45:33,240
without counting your mistakes, without feeling guilty.

408
00:45:48,984 --> 00:45:53,100
Now, stretch your hand

409
00:45:53,707 --> 00:45:55,620
straight,

410
00:45:56,585 --> 00:46:00,153
and put your centre of your palm

411
00:46:00,354 --> 00:46:02,740
on top of your head.

412
00:46:03,760 --> 00:46:07,180
Bend your head, stretch your fingers

413
00:46:07,380 --> 00:46:09,340
and press your scalp,

414
00:46:09,540 --> 00:46:13,487
move it seven times slowly.

415
00:46:24,355 --> 00:46:26,420
Bend your head please.

416
00:46:28,186 --> 00:46:31,325
Here also I cannot force you.

417
00:46:31,526 --> 00:46:33,847
So you have to say “Mother,

418
00:46:34,047 --> 00:46:37,919
please give me my Realization”, seven times.

419
00:47:26,938 --> 00:47:29,620
Now, take down your hand.

420
00:47:32,248 --> 00:47:34,260
Please open your eyes.

421
00:47:39,984 --> 00:47:42,780
Now put your right hand towards Me.

422
00:47:48,403 --> 00:47:50,260
Bend your head

423
00:47:52,780 --> 00:47:57,580
and see for yourself if there is a cool breeze coming out of your head.

424
00:48:08,416 --> 00:48:11,979
Now take your left hand like this.

425
00:48:17,669 --> 00:48:21,460
Put your right hand on top of your head

426
00:48:25,094 --> 00:48:28,900
and see for yourself if you are feeling the cool breeze.

427
00:48:32,795 --> 00:48:34,860
Bend your head a little.

428
00:49:00,317 --> 00:49:03,677
Now, again put your right hand towards Me

429
00:49:06,739 --> 00:49:10,739
and see with your left hand if you can feel the cool breeze.

430
00:49:16,076 --> 00:49:18,460
Now raise your both the hands,

431
00:49:20,937 --> 00:49:23,747
high up. Raise your head.

432
00:49:25,179 --> 00:49:28,500
Bend it back and ask the question,

433
00:49:28,700 --> 00:49:32,420
“Mother is this the cool breeze of the Holy Ghost?”

434
00:49:37,076 --> 00:49:41,140
“Mother is this the Brahma Shakti?”

435
00:49:43,947 --> 00:49:48,099
“Mother is this the love of God?”

436
00:49:52,898 --> 00:49:55,098
Ask these questions three times.

437
00:50:04,984 --> 00:50:08,157
Now, bring down your hands please.

438
00:50:09,468 --> 00:50:11,620
Watch Me without thinking.

439
00:50:39,165 --> 00:50:42,700
Now those who have felt the cool breeze

440
00:50:43,733 --> 00:50:46,236
in the hands or in their heads,

441
00:50:46,436 --> 00:50:48,860
please raise both your hands.

442
00:51:02,029 --> 00:51:06,100
Most of those who came two days have got it.

443
00:51:10,277 --> 00:51:12,594
Those who have come only today,

444
00:51:12,794 --> 00:51:14,794
may not have got it.

445
00:51:18,876 --> 00:51:21,693
So many of you have got your Realization.

446
00:51:24,516 --> 00:51:28,460
Now it is now like a sprouting of the seed.

447
00:51:32,800 --> 00:51:34,940
And you have to grow.

448
00:51:36,814 --> 00:51:39,388
We have got a centre here,

449
00:51:39,658 --> 00:51:43,953
where you should meet and grow.

450
00:51:44,153 --> 00:51:47,620
Within one month’s time you will be a master.

451
00:51:58,090 --> 00:52:02,380
You know we don’t take money, so we have very humble place.

452
00:52:07,018 --> 00:52:10,259
And you have to be very humble yourself.

453
00:52:14,136 --> 00:52:16,940
And please see that you all grow.

454
00:52:21,028 --> 00:52:23,900
Some of you did not get Realization

455
00:52:26,711 --> 00:52:29,580
or maybe you did not feel the cool breeze,

456
00:52:31,724 --> 00:52:34,340
but might be feeling peaceful within.

457
00:52:36,793 --> 00:52:41,900
If this centre is out of gear also you don’t feel the vibrations.

458
00:52:47,851 --> 00:52:52,260
If you have not forgiven people, also you don’t feel the vibrations.

459
00:52:57,332 --> 00:53:00,820
So you have to take it up seriously.

460
00:53:04,360 --> 00:53:07,260
You are entering into a new world,

461
00:53:09,269 --> 00:53:12,980
and not to be treated frivolously, childishly.

462
00:53:16,584 --> 00:53:20,801
And I am sure all of you will develop that subtlety

463
00:53:24,898 --> 00:53:27,380
and all the powers

464
00:53:28,754 --> 00:53:32,354
by which you can to do miraculous things.

465
00:53:35,398 --> 00:53:39,163
I am sorry today there is short of time, so I have to go.

466
00:53:39,363 --> 00:53:42,340
But I hope you all will look after yourself.

467
00:53:47,991 --> 00:53:50,180
You have a very good,

468
00:53:50,538 --> 00:53:53,639
wise Sahaja Yogi here,

469
00:53:53,840 --> 00:53:57,700
who is the leader of Spanish people.

470
00:54:02,431 --> 00:54:05,180
You don’t have to spend any money.

471
00:54:07,260 --> 00:54:10,191
Only you have to pay attention to yourself

472
00:54:10,392 --> 00:54:14,992
and you have to attend the center.

473
00:54:22,293 --> 00:54:26,194
You cannot do it individually. It is a collective happening.

474
00:54:31,124 --> 00:54:35,260
Like one tree is supplying sap to all the leaves.

475
00:54:40,050 --> 00:54:43,461
The leaf that develops a bark between

476
00:54:43,661 --> 00:54:46,020
itself and the tree, falls off.

477
00:54:52,458 --> 00:54:54,844
With little patience with yourself,

478
00:54:55,044 --> 00:54:58,928
you will develop that subtle

479
00:55:00,387 --> 00:55:04,220
being within yourself, by which you will

480
00:55:04,420 --> 00:55:08,620
feel the joy of the Divine,

481
00:55:18,763 --> 00:55:20,860
which is your right,

482
00:55:21,909 --> 00:55:24,580
which you all should have.

483
00:55:25,330 --> 00:55:27,330
May God bless you all.

484
00:55:33,012 --> 00:55:37,540
Only thing I have to request, that don’t talk to anyone now.

485
00:55:41,406 --> 00:55:44,580
Please go home in this silence

486
00:55:44,780 --> 00:55:47,420
and don’t discuss and argue.

487
00:55:52,706 --> 00:55:55,380
Because you lose your vibrations.

488
00:55:58,143 --> 00:56:03,300
So I have to request you not to argue it out. You cannot argue it.

489
00:56:06,206 --> 00:56:08,380
It has to work out.

490
00:56:10,242 --> 00:56:13,916
Those who have not got also should not blame anyone.

491
00:56:19,537 --> 00:56:21,537
May God bless you.

492
00:56:27,360 --> 00:56:30,304
Finished at ten o’clock as you said it.

493
00:56:37,595 --> 00:56:39,595
Where are My shoes?

